*DESCRIPTION_START
The trail is nearly invisible in spots, as it wanders south, parallel to the
slope of the hills, through the tall pines that make up this forest. The
ground breaks steeply away to the east, and you can catch glimpses of the
farmland here and there through the trees.
*DESCRIPTION_END
