NUMBER 1116
NAME Clearing, Ruins of Margrave's House
PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The rubble of what used to be a small, metallic house stands amid the pine
trees here, on a level spot on the side of the hill. The bed of a narrow
garden outside what used to be the door grows rampant with a mixture of now-
wild flowers and weeds.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 418 ADJ1=44 ADJ2=592 ADJ3=454
