The burnt-out shell of the house seems to consist of a strange shining
metallic substance that is now twisted and blackened with soot. You can make
out the remains of several windows that lined this side of the building. You
see the shattered remnants of a broken panel of colored glass near what used
to be the door.
*DESCRIPTION_END
