Number 1108
Name West of a Ruin
PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a large pile of rubble to your east. What was once a verdant lawn is
now scarred with deep gashes and the signs of many feet and wheels. The burn
marks of powerful magic, and the bones and broken weapons of undead soldiers
litter the area. To the north, you see the ruins of a small cemetery.
*DESCRIPTION_END
