Name Manor, Inside Gate
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
Once a fertile field, the horror of darkness has forever tainted the ring
of soil surrounding the manor. Ringed by the macabre image of the fence,
and punctuated by the dread manor in the center, you can't help feeling a
slight bit of dread as you gaze about the area. A bird of carrion sits in
a withered apple tree, eyeing you hungrily.
*DESCRIPTION_END
