                        ECHO PLAYER You have found what looks like a narrow trail a short distance off the track. It leads to the northwest.
                ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB northwest -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You brush aside some undergrowth and push your way into the forest to the northwest...
        ECHO OTHERS %N brushes aside some undergrowth and pushes %h way into the forest to the northwest.
        DISBAND
        MOVE 1130
        AFFECT 1130
        ECHO OTHERS Sticks snapping and leaves crunching underfoot, %N appears through some undergrowth to the southeast.
        AFFECT 1129
ENDIF
