; ** Quill Pen
;
INUMBER 344
EQUAL ITEMADJ1 953
NAME 584
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE PAPER
TURNABLE
IFPREVERB TURN -1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER You turn the pen idly in your fingers, deep in thought.
ECHO OTHERS %N turns a quill pen in %h fingers, apparently deep in thought.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DIP -1
CLEARVERB
IFCARRY 1815 25
ECHO PLAYER You dip the pen in the jar of ink, getting just the right amount of ink on the tip.
ECHO OTHERS %N dips the tip of %h pen in an ink jar.
ELSE
ECHO PLAYER You need to get out your ink jar first.
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LICK -1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER You moisten the tip of the quill with your tongue.
ECHO OTHERS %N touches the tip of a quill pen to %h tongue.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER The pen flows effortlessly across your parchment.
ECHO OTHERS %N writes something down on a piece of parchement.
ENDIF
