                                        ELSE
                                                ECHO PLAYER You stumble over your feet, botching your attempt to sneak into the alley.
                                                ECHO OTHERS %N ducks into an alleyway.
                                                DISBAND
                                                MOVE ITEMVAL2
                                                AFFECT ITEMVAL2
                                                ECHO OTHERS %N appears through an alleyway.
                                        ENDIF
                                ENDIF
                        ENDIF
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
